graph TD
    A[Input Image 3x224x224] --> B[Conv2d: 16x224x224]
    B --> C[ReLU Activation]
    C --> D[MaxPool2d: 16x112x112]
    D --> E[Feature Map Output]
    
    subgraph ResNet Intuition
    E --> F[Conv Layer 1]
    F --> G[Conv Layer 2]
    E -.->|Residual / Skip Connection| G
    G --> H[ReLU]
    end
